      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-8">
        <p>SCOTLAND: The Big Picture is rewriting nature’s story, seeking to return abundance and diversity of life to Scotland’s land and seas, so that wildlife can flourish and people thrive.</p>
        <p>Be part of the conversation and make some noise. Share SCOTLAND: The Big Picture's rewilding stories, visit local rewilding initiatives, and gain a better understanding, or a new perspective.</p>
        <p><strong>Seasgair are proud to:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Sponsor local rewilding projects</li>
          <li>Make a donation each time a guest buys a Spa Pack</li>
          <li>Help raise awareness and share the story</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Be inspired, be involved. What you can do:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Download and enjoy <%= link_to 'Pinelands', 'https://www.scotlandbigpicture.com/Store/ebooks/ebook-pinelands', target: :_blank, class: 'green-link' %>, a book packed full of stunning photography and powerful images of Scottish nature</li>
          <li>Watch the <%= link_to 'Scottish Rewilding Alliance animation', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZR2sPQHUt_4', target: :_blank, class: 'green-link' %>
          </li>
          <li>Put wild into your everyday life. Begin to make small changes - <%= link_to 'MeWilding', 'https://www.scotlandbigpicture.com/Store/ebooks/mewilding-ebook', target: :_blank, class: 'green-link' %> is rewilding for everyone!</li>
          <li>Donate via the <%= link_to 'Seasgair Community Giving Page', 'https://www.scotlandbigpicture.com/donate-SeasgairLodges', target: :_blank, class: 'green-link' %></li>
        </ul>
